<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.0.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm">Written Answers Tuesday 13 October 2009</major-heading>

<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.1.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm">Scottish Executive</major-heading>

<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28079.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">Ministerial Meetings</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28079.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80283" speakername="Jackie Baillie (Dumbarton) (Lab)" spid="S3W-28079" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive how many times the Joint Strategic Review of Public Spending has met.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28079.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80397" speakername="John Swinney" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">

  <p>The Joint Strategic Review of Public Spending has met twice and I wrote to the members of the review group in August to propose that further meetings should be held following the publication of the draft 2010-11 Budget document on 17 September 2009.</p>

</reply>


<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28080.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">Ministerial Meetings</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28080.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80283" speakername="Jackie Baillie (Dumbarton) (Lab)" spid="S3W-28080" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive how often the Cabinet Secretary for Finance and Sustainable Growth has attended meetings of the Joint Strategic Review of Public Spending.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-10-13.S3W-28080.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80397" speakername="John Swinney" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa1013.htm#1">

  <p>I have chaired both meetings of the Joint Strategic Review held to date and have written to all members to propose that further meetings should be held over the autumn.</p>

</reply>
